wiki.summary: Don Toliver reunites with Justin Bieber and Future on “Private Landing,” the ninth track from his third studio album, Love Sick. The three artists boast about their women, drug usage, and expensive jewelry over a banging beat. On February 20, 2023, Don teased a snippet of the song in the fourth episode of a video series he created for the album. In a now-deleted tweet that same day, music news Twitter user OnThinIce stated that Justin would be featured on it alongside another artist yet to be announced. Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: Don Toliver reunites with Justin Bieber and Future on “Private Landing,” the ninth track from his third studio album, Love Sick. The three artists boast about their women, drug usage, and expensive jewelry over a banging beat. On February 20, 2023, Don teased a snippet of the song in the fourth episode of a video series he created for the album. In a now-deleted tweet that same day, music news Twitter user OnThinIce stated that Justin would be featured on it alongside another artist yet to be announced. Three days later, Don made comic book-style posts for the album on social media, in which he revealed which artists would be featured on which track, in which in one, he confirmed this to be true and revealed that Future would be the second featured artist on it.
